sentence.text: An analysis of human SCLC specimens revealed that negative regulation by host of viral transcription is expressed exclusively in variant SCLC tumors that lack expression of neuroendocrine markers and instead express markers of a chemosensory lineage known as tuft cells.

entity.text: negative regulation by host of viral transcription

sentence.text: Moreover, we show that most SCLC tumors can be classified into one of three lineages based on the expression of negative regulation by host of viral transcription, ASCL1, or NEUROD1.
